import Container from "@mui/material/Container";
import Grid from "@mui/material/Grid";
import Card from "@mui/material/Card";
import MKBox from "components/MKBox";
import MKTypography from "components/MKTypography";
import MKButton from "components/MKButton";
import Header from "components/Header";
import Footer from "components/Footer";

function BecomeSponsor() {
  return (
    <>
      <Header />
      <MKBox sx={{ paddingTop: "60px" }} bgcolor="white">
        {/* Hero Section */}
        <MKBox
          minHeight="50vh"
          width="100%"
          sx={{
            backgroundImage: `linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('/images/soccer-feet.jpg')`,
            backgroundSize: "cover",
            backgroundPosition: "center",
            display: "grid",
            placeItems: "center",
          }}
        >
          <Container>
            <Grid container justifyContent="center" textAlign="center">
              <Grid item xs={12} md={8}>
                <MKTypography variant="h1" color="white" mb={3}>
                  Become a Sponsor
                </MKTypography>
                <MKTypography variant="body1" color="white" mb={3}>
                  Help transform young lives through soccer
                </MKTypography>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Container>
        </MKBox>

        {/* Sponsorship Options */}
        <Container sx={{ py: 6 }}>
          <Grid container spacing={3}>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
              <Card sx={{ p: 3, height: "100%" }}>
                <MKTypography variant="h4" mb={2}>
                  Basic Sponsor
                </MKTypography>
                <MKTypography variant="h2" mb={2}>
                  $500
                </MKTypography>
                {/* Add sponsorship details */}
              </Card>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
              <Card sx={{ p: 3, height: "100%" }}>
                <MKTypography variant="h4" mb={2}>
                  Premium Sponsor
                </MKTypography>
                <MKTypography variant="h2" mb={2}>
                  $1000
                </MKTypography>
                {/* Add sponsorship details */}
              </Card>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
              <Card sx={{ p: 3, height: "100%" }}>
                <MKTypography variant="h4" mb={2}>
                  Elite Sponsor
                </MKTypography>
                <MKTypography variant="h2" mb={2}>
                  $2000
                </MKTypography>
                {/* Add sponsorship details */}
              </Card>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Container>
      </MKBox>
      <Footer />
    </>
  );
}

export default BecomeSponsor;
